To request a specific map or for more information, contact a reference librarian in the Geography & Map Division (202) 707-6277 or through the "Ask a librarian" link through the Geography & Map Division website https://www.loc.gov/rr/geogmap/.
Title supplied by cataloger.
If a map in this collection may be in copyright, there is no online image available.
Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image.
